<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/alan-mak> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Alan Mak was a Parliamentary Under Secretary of State jointly in the Department for Business and Trade and the Cabinet Office between 26 March 2024 and 5 July 2024. He was Exchequer Secretary to the Treasury between 8 July 2022 and 8 September 2022. He was previously Government Whip (Lord Commissioner of HM Treasury) between 21 April 2021 to 8 July 2022."@en .
